entries.npc_10: Hope you can do that on your own.
entries.npc_9: Don't worry about what I think.
entries.npc_8: Good, I hope you can find your way out of here.
entries.npc_6: Sorry.  I'll try to be more pleasant in the future.
entries.npc_4: Well as slick as you are I'm surprised you haven't found ALL the rebels on Tatooine.
entries.npc_3: I don't know where you would have heard such a rumor.
entries.player_10: Don't have many friends do you?
entries.player_9: Guess I'll pack up and go then.
entries.player_8: Don't think I've fallen for your tricks...
entries.player_7: I guess I'll be on my way.
entries.player_6: Sorry, I have you confused with someone else.
entries.player_5: It's ok, I'm not with the Empire...
entries.npc_2: Yes, I know.  I am actually PART of the family.  It's not just Biggs you know!
entries.player_2: Aren't you part of the rebellion?
entries.player_1: I've heard of your family.  They're famous.
entries.npc_1: Hello.  My name is Dera Darklighter.  Is there something I can do for you?
